&lt;p class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;He was surely lower than anyone else had ever climbed: he was entering the upper stratum of the mists...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By &lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php?option=com_content&amp;amp;view=article&amp;amp;id=107&amp;amp;catid=31&amp;amp;Itemid=101&quot;&gt;Andy Robertson&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;story-intro&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-days-of-darkening/75-above-part-1&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;story-thumb&quot; src=&quot;https://nightland.website/images/thumbs/armitage-black-canyon-from-chasm-view-gunnison-pd-altered-thumb.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;A deep canyon with nearly vertical sides, formed of dark rock with a magenta cast.&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;He was surely lower than anyone else had ever climbed: he was entering the upper stratum of the mists...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
