		<content type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By &lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/background/authors-and-artists/107-andy-robertson&quot;&gt;Andy Robertson&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
