	<entry>
		<title>Delight (Part 4)</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-days-of-darkening/46-delight/100-delight-part-4"/>
		<published>2015-05-06T19:02:12+00:00</published>
		<updated>2015-05-06T19:02:12+00:00</updated>
		<id>https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/night-land-stories/the-days-of-darkening/46-delight/100-delight-part-4</id>
		<author>
			<name>Kate Coady</name>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By &lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/background/authors-and-artists/107-andy-robertson&quot;&gt;Andy Robertson&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;story-intro&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/34-night-land-stories/the-days-of-darkening/100-delight-part-4&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;story-thumb&quot; src=&quot;https://nightland.website/images/thumbs/coady-red-sun-thumb.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;A red sky over a cobblestone road that leads past alien plants toward a land of lava.&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;The land reaching into that shadow, north of the road, was overgrown with the strange crystal flower patterns that she was now used to seeing, and warped in other ways. In some places it reared up into shapes like animals, or human faces or limbs, or distorted machine parts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By &lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/background/authors-and-artists/107-andy-robertson&quot;&gt;Andy Robertson&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;story-intro&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/stories/34-night-land-stories/the-days-of-darkening/100-delight-part-4&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;story-thumb&quot; src=&quot;https://nightland.website/images/thumbs/coady-red-sun-thumb.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;A red sky over a cobblestone road that leads past alien plants toward a land of lava.&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;The land reaching into that shadow, north of the road, was overgrown with the strange crystal flower patterns that she was now used to seeing, and warped in other ways. In some places it reared up into shapes like animals, or human faces or limbs, or distorted machine parts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
