		<content type="html">&lt;h3 class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;By &lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/about/authors-and-artists/154-carole-carmen&quot;&gt;Carole Carmen&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
